'''梅爾'''（Mere）是位於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[威爾特郡|威爾特郡]]的一個小鎮和民政教區。A303公路途徑這裡<ref>{{cite web|website=Wiltshire Community History|title=Mere|url=http://history.wiltshire.gov.uk/community/getcom.php?id=160|publisher=Wiltshire Council|accessdate=30 December 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081956/http://history.wiltshire.gov.uk/community/getcom.php?id=160|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。這裡的主要名勝有聖米歇爾教堂<ref>{{cite web|title=Mere, St Michael the Archangel|publisher=Salisbury Diocesan Guild of Ringers|url=http://sdgr.org.uk/tower/?tower=mere|accessdate=2 January 2016|archive-date=2016-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401054227/http://sdgr.org.uk/tower/?tower=mere|dead-url=no}}</ref>和伍德蘭茲莊園等<ref>{{National Heritage List for England|num=1200753|desc=Woodlands Manor|access-date=3 January 2016|fewer-links=yes}}</ref>。

